Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到这股心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上双眼用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:14.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,满溢的热气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那一日的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:34.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,苏醒的追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,katharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:42.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吧 将一切解放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着未来跑动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,名为青涩和你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻就传达到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,强而有力地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:59.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝那倾洒而出的光芒 伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:06.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,So Just Light Bravest Destiny
